> > off a 78 Which I think are the same"
>
> almost positive they changed in 72/73 so they would not be directly
> interchangeable,

You can use these parts on a '71, but you have to swap the spindle,
caliper, hub, and rotor as a set.  You get longer-lasting (but not
stronger) brakes in the bargain.

George Lyle

